  <brief_title>Tranexamic Acid in Preventing Postpartum Hemorrhage in High Risk Pregnancies During Elective Cesarean Section</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effect of Tranexamic Acid in Preventing Postpartum Hemorrhage in High Risk Pregnancies During Elective Cesarean Section, a Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
