  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      postpartum hemorrhage (PPT) represents one of the major causes of maternal mortality .
      Tranexamic acid is used in many studies in management of PPH in combination with ecobolics.
      this study aims to evaluate the possible value of the use of tranexamic acid in prevention of
      postpartum hemorrhage .
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
