    <intervention_name>Tranexamic Acid</intervention_name>
    <description>Tranexamic acid (Kepron, Amoun, Egypt) was given slowly intravenously over 10 minutes just before the skin incision of elective cesarean section to group A. Tranexamic acid injection was prepared by diluting 1g (10 mL) tranexamic acid into 20 ml of 5% glucose.</description>
